title: Was that from our wallets. I've given you 3 stalls to reach out too. I have some special digital IDS I need copies of as well as you to have someone contact me or whomever is sitting in until I leave. They can pull up to the house.
body: This should only be used in very rare cases e.g. if you are not 100% sure if something is a bug or asking a question that leads to improving the documentation. For general questions please use [Erigon's discord](https://discord.gg/hQ2dxbNZ).

Do you mean the card attached or the one at esporta? I destroyed both of them per instructions for non-metal cards? I then took this copy to chase cybersecurity at Travure across from Microsoft sales in Memphis TN. He wrote for YOU to bring me a new card since the only shipping method is FIS global. Attached should be my group #, access ID, PIN number, and revolving credit limit and replenish instructions.
I’ll be at 1919 malabar drive germantown TN 38138 when you’re ready. My phone # is 9015626091 and my authorization code is *117*****. As well as *473******. Both of which are printed on google open source api. Well secure as soon as contractor or military personnel pick me up for transport to guarded lodging.

-Brian LaZek
